# 📝 StudyMate Task Manager App

## 📌 Overview
This is a Task Management Android application built using Kotlin, Room Database, and MVVM architecture. It supports full CRUD operations.

---

## 🏗 Architecture
The app follows MVVM pattern:

- Model: Room Entity (Task)
- View: UI Screens (Jetpack Compose / XML)
- ViewModel: Business logic
- Repository: Data abstraction layer

---

## 🗄 Room Database Setup
Room is used for offline local storage.

---

## ⚙ Features

- Add new tasks
- Update existing tasks
- Delete tasks
- View all tasks
- Offline storage using Room
- Clean MVVM architecture

---

## 🚀 Tech Stack

- Kotlin
- Android Jetpack
- Room Database (FIREBASE)
- MVVM Architecture
- LiveData
- Coroutines

